You decided to give me plenty of reason to do otherwise.<br>
<br>
You keep harping on this theory that I was behind all your problems, and the Isengard is the evil behind everyone hating you.<br>
<br>
WAKE THE FUCK UP!  We were angry that someone stole from us, we tried to get you to do something, and you did *nothing* for weeks!  We got over it, we moved on!  We had no 'evil conspiracy' that was out to get Rthen!<br>
<br>
  Maybe a few members who had been directly involved were still pissed at you and decided to harrass you from time to time because you were an ignorant lethargic pussy who didn't want to take any action, but that didn't mean the rest of the entire guild had ANYTHING to do with it. <br>
<br>
 We had better things to do with our time than spend it taking shots at a huge, slow-moving target.  Select other people on the server who decided you deserved their attention thought differently I guess.  That's where your problems really started.  I and my compatriots moved on years ago!  ... That is, I had until you decided to respond  with vitriol to my attempts to show you reason. <br>
<br>
Good luck ever finding anyone here to sympathize with you again.<br>
<br>
 Zandramas<br>
